Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:09.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Earthland, in the \Noutskirts of Magnolia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:23.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:01.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:03.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of Magnolia is, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:04.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:05.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:06.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to rejoice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:09.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to make sure everyone is safe, first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:10.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:14.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We got to Earthland a bit before you, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:17.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already flown around a bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:20.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The people in the guild \Nand the city are all safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:25.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like none of them even realize \Nthey were turned into a lacrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:26.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Earthland sure is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:28.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's magic {\i1}everywhere{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:34.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Why are the Exceeds in Earthland?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:40.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:45.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:49.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We should return them to Edolas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:53.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:55.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Extalia's gone, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:57.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive them, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:58.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:03:00.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I threw stones at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:01.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:04.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, we don't have any place to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:06.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll change our ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:07.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:09.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:15.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sent me to Earthland with orders \Nto eliminate the Dragon Slayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:19.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen stole our eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:21.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't ever gonna forget that, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:23.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:24.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:28.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if you tell us to go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:35.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We never really explained carefully, did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:38.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This story goes back 6 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:42.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe we've mentioned \Nhow the Queen, Chagot,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:46.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,has the power to see the future, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:47.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:55.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Extalia is falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:04:00.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Queen saw such a vision, \Nthere can be no mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:04.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Such violence... The only ones \Nwho could do such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking back on it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:14.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it was probably the drying up of magic power \Nthat would cause the islands to fall naturally...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:17.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, at the time, we thought the \Ncause would surely be the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:25.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We would not win a war against the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:32.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll evacuate the children...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:33.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Evacuate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:35.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:44.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's not exactly... \Nwhat you told us before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:51.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This plan was kept secret even \Nfrom the citizens of Extalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:56.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Queen lied... She put on an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:05.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a plan to destroy monsters from \Nanother world... The Dragon Slayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:08.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I wish for everyone to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:15.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Having the Queen lie like \Nthat pained my heart so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:17.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We had no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:22.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How could we say publicly that \NExtalia would crash into the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:28.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, we had no particular \Ngrudge against Dragon Slayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:29.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:33.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You needed to create a \Nconvincing story, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:38.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, if you told the truth \NI'm sure everyone would panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:39.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:49.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We borrowed the human's Anima, \Nand our plan was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:51.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:58.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There was just one thing that \Nhappened we didn't account for...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:04.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was... your power, Carla.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:10.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a similar power to mine \Nthat can predict the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:21.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you seem to activate it subconsciously \Nand confuse it with your own memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:26.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the 100 Exceeds that evacuated...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:35.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect you're the only one who \Nforesaw fragments of Edolas's future...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:39.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is for the Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:44.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic power in this world is vanishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:49.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The children are for defeating \Nthe Dragon Slayers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is their mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:59.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And, it seems like you \Nmistook it for your mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:03.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:06.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There never was such a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:16.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad luck piled up and you somehow created \Na non-existent mission for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:23.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was all seeing the future, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:29.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We took advantage of the fact that \Nyou didn't know your own power
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:33.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,by making you think you \Nwere being manipulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:39.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all an act to maintain \Nthe majesty of the Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I truly apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:48.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Much bad luck, and the false \Nfront I had to show the citizens,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,combined to cause you great suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:54.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And moreover, six years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:59.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,when I stole up the eggs from people's \Nfamilies, I caused incredible sorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:07.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I handed you that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:10.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not the Exceed as \Na whole who are at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:12.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is I alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:20.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:23.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:28.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you did, Queen, \Nyou did looking out for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:33.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we were overconfident in ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're here in Earthland and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:40.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...let's go search for the children \Nwho evacuated here 6 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:46.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've discovered a new goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:48.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, let's get along with the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:50.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our big new start!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:54.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward-looking bunch, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:56.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:03.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A new beginning... What a wonderful \Nthing to be able to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:07.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:18.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why do I have the same power you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:21.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:23.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:24.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice weather we're having...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're acting weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:27.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:30.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think the Queen and \NCarla look kinda similar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:35.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! You know, like how they move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:36.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How they move?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See, like that part!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:41.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What part is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:44.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm just glad that ended \Nwith everyone safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:45.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it looks like you \Ncaught it from him, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:48.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So did you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:55.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment, what beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:57.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a lovely parfum!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:58.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:09:59.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:02.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to smell more of your parfum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How cruel... And after all I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:12.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... You reminded me of someone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:17.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we'll live near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:19.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can see each other any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:21.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you so happy about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:22.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:29.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can see each other \Nwhenever we want, Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:30.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Qu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:37.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:41.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over and play whenever \Nyou'd like, Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:42.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:44.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like I'm expectin' ya to, or anythin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:48.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the way you two smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:49.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:56.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a hundred years too young \Nto start smelling me, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:03.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:04.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:07.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:09.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:12.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:14.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate these depressin' farewells.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:16.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.87,0:11:19.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come play anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:23.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:24.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:26.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely parfum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:28.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:35.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell her you're her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:42.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until every child I sent to be \Nevacuated 6 years ago is found,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:46.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no right to claim that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:48.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:52.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A greenhorn like that ain't no son-o-mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:54.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see him whenever \Nyou'd like now, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:58.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know your own daughter \Nwas in one of those eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:07.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just Queen in name only.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:12.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For a parent, one's child \Nis always the most precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:15.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't argue with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:18.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:20.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's return to our guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How should we report this to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:27.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, no one noticed what happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:30.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't keep quiet about \Nwhat happened to Mystogan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone... Your hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:34.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:37.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Gajeel? You wanna do it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:38.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was a point to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:42.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Lily?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:45.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't seen Panther Lily around anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:49.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That super-strong Exceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:51.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me, I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:57.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:06.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:08.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure got cutesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:12.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems as if Earthland does not \Nmatch well with my constitution.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:15.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're okay there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:20.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I want to join this \Nguild that took care of the Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:24.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll keep your promise and \Nget me in? Right, Gajeel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:30.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I will, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:31.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:37.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, about another matter... \NI caught someone suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A big catch right off the bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:41.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my cat for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:41.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:46.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not... anyone... suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:50.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:57.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a member of Fairy Tail, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:00.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:04.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this cat? Are you an Exceed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:06.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Panther Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:10.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's yer problem? You \Ntalkin' crap 'bout my cat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:13.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:18.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My... Somehow Edolas's Lisanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:21.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...came with us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:22.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:31.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:44.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, I get to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:47.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to see the real Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:54.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Gray, Erza... How long has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:01.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this brings back so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:04.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These are new guild members, I gather?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:06.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A little Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:08.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:12.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec... Don't tell me you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:14.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...our Lisanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:20.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:27.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You came back from the dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:30.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:34.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We all thought you died two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:37.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you've \Ncome back from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:44.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:47.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:51.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna, open your eyes, Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:54.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:56.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening? Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:58.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:15:59.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:01.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:03.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:14.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect that I was sucked \Ninto an Anima then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:20.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, there should have been a lot \Nof small Anima around Earthland, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:26.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I came to in Edolas, I was shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:29.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:36.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was a little different, but \Nthere were familiar faces right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:41.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, everyone assumed \NI was Edolas's Lisanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:48.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured that Edolas's \NLisanna had already died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:52.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell from the way \Nthe guild treated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:56.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna's alive, Nee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:17:00.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you fell from so high up... \NI thought you were done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:07.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't understand at the time, \Nbut when I think about it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:14.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,perhaps the Anima was trying to \Ncomplete something Edolas lacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:17.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,by sucking me up when their Lisanna died...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:21.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go anywhere ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:24.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:25.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't say the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:33.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I pretended to be Edolas's Lisanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:37.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:48.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was unsure at first, but \Nsoon my memories got jumbled,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:51.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and I learned bit by bit about Edolas...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:57.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with everyone, I got used \Nto the way of life in Edolas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.75,0:17:59.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, after two years passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:04.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Six days ago Earthland \NNatsu and Happy showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:06.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:14.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell us the truth then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:28.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying you've come from \Nanother world called Earthland?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:30.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Lisannna?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:38.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:41.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Natsu and Happy I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:44.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let them find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:50.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to make Mira-nee and \NElf-niichan sad ever again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:52.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to get through this..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:58.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to live on here in Edolas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:02.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:05.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:06.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:10.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's not it, everyone! I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:16.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay... We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:27.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about not saying that we realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:35.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a kind girl, just like \Nour Lisanna that died...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:41.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you mustn't make your real big \Nbrother and sister cry any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:46.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-nee... Elf-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:50.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to the world you came from, Lisanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:53.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give our best wishes to the \NEarthland versions of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:20:04.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-nee!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:20.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Earthland... Kardia Cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:35.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan, we should get going...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:36.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:48.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:51.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:54.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:39.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:49.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:21:59.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:22.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:23:59.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's strange... Where'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:00.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:03.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing I left out for \Na snack today is all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.61,0:24:06.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been leaving stuff \Nout all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:08.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you leave out?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.12,0:24:11.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had flames left over from last night's \Ndinner, so I put 'em into a tin...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.59,0:24:13.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But now it's totally empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.92,0:24:16.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: That Which Erases Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.92,0:24:20.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... Mira put it out, \Nsaying it could start a fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.89,0:24:22.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was her!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.35,0:24:24.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with Mira on this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.11,0:24:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
